    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a museum-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a flawless double-VANOS system. This chassis has undergone a proactive subframe reinforcement and remains free of any stress fractures or fatigue. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox operates with crisp, tactile engagement, delivering power through a perfectly calibrated limited-slip differential. Every bushing, ball joint, and control arm remains in peak operating condition, ensuring the original suspension geometry is preserved. The engine bay retains its factory cosmoline, and compression tests show nominal, consistent values across all six cylinders. This is a rare, mechanically sorted specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Full service records. Garage kept. No accidents. Original paint. Inspection welcome.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior features a flawless, deep-gloss finish protected by a professional ceramic coating, with absolutely no chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather still retains its original scent and firm texture, while every electronic component and switch functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a complete, documented maintenance history. The alloy wheels are free of any curb rash and are wrapped in high-performance tires with near-full tread. This is a turn-key, investment-grade example for a buyer who demands the absolute best.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
